      "content": "oh wow okay, that sounds serious. but he's really stubborn about it... he says he's just dehydrated and wants to just sleep it off for a few hours to see if he wakes up feeling better. he's also really worried about the cost of an ambulance and the hassle of the ER if it's just travel fatigue. do you think it's really worth the huge hospital bill if it's just from the jet lag? could we just give him some electrolytes and let him rest?",
